   WITH: TRAVEL BRIEFS: Now you can always have Paris _ sort of _
even if you never get to France. New York, Venice, Monte Carlo and
Luxor have all been paid homage in the form of Las Vegas hotels, so
the Paris Las Vegas Casino Resort seemed overdue.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BOOKS &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   PAGE INCLUDES FIVE COLOR PHOTOS AND ONE B&AMP;W ILLUSTRATION
</P>
