   &QL; 
 &QL; 
Weather insurance
</P>
<P>
   For those considering a Caribbean vacation during hurricane
season _ now through the end of October _ it might be comforting to
know that some resorts offer a vacation guarantee against stormy
weather. At the Four Seasons Resort Nevis through September, guests
receive a full refund of their deposit plus a refund of the land
portion of the cost of the resort's package or guestroom for days
affected by a storm. For information, call 800-332-3442.
</P>
<P>
   Superclubs also provides a hurricane guarantee at all its clubs
in the Bahamas and Jamaica. In addition, it offers a sunshine
guarantee in Jamaica _ any time the sun doesn't show its face any
day during a Jamaican vacation, the club issues a voucher equal to
that day's value, good for one year toward another SuperClub
vacation. For information, call 800-GO SUPER (800-467-8737)
</P>
