Feb. 5, 2000 (excluding Dec. 17-Jan. 1) when booking a six-night
vacation. SuperClubs has a variety of all-inclusive clubs on
Jamaica ranging from moderate-priced Breezes to luxurious Grand
Lido Resorts to party-loving Hedonism Resorts, along with Boscobel
Beach, a family-oriented resort.
</P>
