along the coast from Vero Beach to St. Augustine. However, The Post
has moved its press start to 4 a.m. EDT so it can print and deliver
the paper after the storm has passed (the worst is expected to hit
between 8 p.m. and midnight). Deadlines have been moved back, so
only sidebars are expected early.
