   FBN-INJURIES _ Some of the most high-profile players in the NFL
were injured on the opening weekend, and most of the injuries are
being viewed as artificial turf related. Each year when the NFL
does its survey of players, artificial turf is the No. 1 complaint.
The league has dragged its feet with the issue, but even domed
stadiums _ the Superdome in preseason _ are experimenting with
playing on grass indoors. (Schlabach, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 22.
