his now-5-year-old car doesn't have much of a chance to win the
second Petit Le Mans. More perplexing, his Doyle-Risi team still
hasn't heard any news of an upgrade from Ferrari, yet he's
surprisingly upbeat because of the success of the American Le Mans
Series. (Mitchell, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
