<P>
   (NYT7) UNDATED -- Sept. 14, 1999 -- KITCHEN-WARES, 09-14 -- Savu
Original Food Smoker Bags make smoked dishes feasible at home. You
take fish fillets, chicken or steaks, and lay them in a shallow
