<P>
   (NYT3) WASHINGTON -- Sept. 14, 1999 -- TIMOR-U.S., 09-13 -- Gen.
Hugh Shelton during his testimony before the Senate Armed Services
Committee last week which was conducting a hearing on his
re-appointment for a new term as chairman of the Joints Chief of
