<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Saturday, Sept.
11, about people in East Timor who are seeking refuge from the
violence there misspelled the surname of the Namibian
representative to the United Nations, who led a delegation that
traveled to East Timor. He is Martin Andjaba, not Adjaba.  &QL;
